      </li>
      <li>
        to attempt to reverse engineer, extract or replicate any underlying
        models or systems; or
      </li>
      <li>in any way that infringes the rights of any third party.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      6.2 You are responsible for reviewing and validating all Output generated
