    <h2>8. Duration and Withdrawal</h2>
    <p>
      8.1 This Addendum takes effect when you enable or use any AI Feature and
      continues until you disable them or cease using the Services.
    </p>

    <h2>9. Changes to this Addendum</h2>
    <p>
      9.1 We may update or modify this Addendum from time to time to reflect
      changes in its AI Features, applicable law, or business practices. The
      revised version will take effect upon posting or notification to you,
